## Data Structures

### Book

+ id (number, required)
+ title (required)
+ author (Author, required)
+ description (required)
+ numOfPages (number, required)
+ year (number, required)
+ cover (object, required)

### Author

Creator of books.

+ id (number, required)
+ name (required)
+ birth (number, required)
+ numOfBooks (number, required)

### BookCreate

+ title (required)
+ author (number, required)
+ description
+ numOfPages (number)
+ year (number)

### BookPartialUpdate

Data transfer object for partially updating an existing Book (PATCH operation).

+ title (required)
+ author_id (number, required)
+ description (required)
+ numOfPages (number, required)
+ year (number, required)
+ cover (object, required)
